{"TopicId":213613,"ForumId":121,"TopicTitle":"Spaceplane base","CreatedByName":"Rocket builder","CreatedById":222181,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T12:52:03Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Rocket builder","CreatedById":222181,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T12:52:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:22px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETHE \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EBASE\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThere\u0027s a pretty hard mission for whoever likes \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003Essto\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003Es\u003C/span\u003E\u00A0and bases, that could look very simple, but surely it isn\u0027t: make a spaceplane that also functions as a base, it has to be pretty big and totally retractible, to complete\u00A0 it I simply advice you to use all of your creativity.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EEnjoy the mission and if you want share your footage.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Socraticat","CreatedById":176118,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-28T19:34:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo this is right up my alley, but what constitutes \u0022functions as a base\u0022? A certain number of kerbals? Number of docking ports? A certain amount of fuel, perhaps?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the meantime, here\u0027s a video I just sped up of my favorite KSP \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E build. It comes complete with an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022In-Situ Resource Utilization\u0022\u003EISRU\u003C/abbr\u003E:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www